text.text: This source leverages an edge-to-edge, responsive layout and is perfect for creative, modern looking websites. Use the Branding Wizard to modify main colors and logo, then drag and drop some components to fill it out with content.

title.jcr:title: This is a Content Container component

text.text: In the edit dialog, define some basic properties of your container like title and styling. Keep in mind that colors can be easily customized through the Branding Wizard. Then, put any components you want inside the container and switch to Layout mode to adjust sizes.
